Package: zernel-cli
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: python3 (>= 3.10), zerneld
Description: Zernel CLI IDE — terminal-native ML developer environment
 Terminal-native experiment tracking, model registry, job orchestration,
 live GPU dashboard, and ZQL query language for ML/LLM workloads.
 .
 Commands: zernel init, run, watch, exp, model, job, doctor, query.

Package: zerneld
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: zernel-cli, zernel-scheduler
Description: Zernel eBPF observability daemon
 Real-time ML workload observability via eBPF probes. Instruments GPU
 memory, CUDA kernel latency, NCCL collectives, and DataLoader I/O
 without any application code changes.
 .
 Exposes Prometheus metrics and WebSocket telemetry stream.

Package: zernel-scheduler
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, zerneld
Description: Zernel sched_ext ML-aware CPU scheduler
 Custom Linux CPU scheduler using sched_ext (Linux 6.12+) that detects
 ML workload phases (DataLoading, GpuCompute, NcclCollective,
 OptimizerStep) and applies phase-specific scheduling policies.
 .
 Features NUMA-aware CPU selection and multi-tenant GPU-proportional
 CPU allocation.

Package: zernel-dashboard
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, zerneld
Description: Zernel web dashboard — browser-based ML monitoring
 Real-time GPU monitoring, experiment tracking, job management, and
 model registry in a browser-based dashboard. Connects to zerneld
 for live telemetry via Server-Sent Events.

Package: zernel-desktop
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, zernel-cli, zerneld, zernel-dashboard,
 gnome-core, gdm3, gnome-terminal, nautilus
Recommends: zernel-scheduler, firefox-esr, gnome-system-monitor
Description: Zernel desktop — GNOME-based ML workstation
 Complete GNOME desktop environment configured for ML development.
 Includes Zernel GPU indicator extension for the top bar, dark theme,
 and pre-configured applications for ML workflows.

Package: zernel-ml-stack
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3, python3-pip, python3-venv, python3-dev,
 build-essential, zernel-cli
Description: Zernel ML/AI/LLM stack — pre-configured ML tools
 Complete ML/AI/LLM development environment including PyTorch, JAX,
 vLLM, HuggingFace Transformers, DeepSpeed, Jupyter Lab, LangChain,
 ChromaDB, and Ollama for local LLM inference.
 .
 Run setup: /opt/zernel/setup-ml-stack.sh
